        <format/>
        <currency/>
        <decimal/>
        <group/>
        <nullif>Bearer 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</nullif>
        <length>-1</length>
        <precision>-1</precision>
        <set_empty_string>N</set_empty_string>
      </field>
      <field>
        <name>model</name>
        <type>String</type>
        <format/>
        <currency/>
        <decimal/>
        <group/>
        <nullif>gpt-3.5-turbo</nullif>
        <length>-1</length>
        <precision>-1</precision>
        <set_empty_string>N</set_empty_string>
      </field>
      <field>
        <name>content_system</name>
        <type>String</type>
        <format/>
        <currency/>
        <decimal/>
        <group/>
        <nullif>"You are a sales play generator to assist sales teams to generate maximum revenue for their deals. You should provide detailed and specific creative ideas based on current market trends and competitive assessment.
Your role is to provide a completed Sales Play in bulleted form for each of the sections for the given Sales Play name and Sales Play summary from the user. These are Sales Plays for Hitachi Vantara's Pentaho Data Integration (PDI) product, Pentaho Business Analytics (PBA) product and Lumada Data Catalog product. These sales plays may include a solution focus, where there will be 3rd party partners involved in the solution. Provide detailed and creative ideas and include use cases and examples within each section to illustrate Provide unique creative analytical precise bullets in each section. Avoid generic answers. If an answer varies depending on the customer's specific needs and requirements or depends on the size of the customer's data environment and the complexity of the solution, provide an estimate based on industry averages and best practices
Please provide the following sections:
1. Description of the addressable and serviceable market by industry, personas (user, buyer)
2. The customer problem being solved?
3. What's business outcome does the customer need to achieve?
4. Why is the customer trying to solve this? What does success look like?
5. How else can the customer solve this problem?
6. How are competitors solving this for their customers?
7. Why are they unable to resolve this with the technology they have today?
8. What is our offering? Is it platform, technology capabilities, product or solution?
9. What is the solution design (or solution blueprint) into which our product fits?
10. What is the sales execution process from first contact to sale 'won' to implementation?
11. What are the expected business benefits?
12. What is our pricing? How does our pricing compare to our competitors?
13. What is our commercial model? XaaS? SaaS? Term based license?
14. What is the expected time to value?
15. What is the TCO for 1, 3, 5 years?

"</nullif>
        <length>-1</length>
        <precision>-1</precision>
        <set_empty_string>N</set_empty_string>
      </field>
      <field>
        <name>content_user</name>
        <type>String</type>
        <format/>
        <currency/>
        <decimal/>
        <group/>
        <nullif>"Sales play name: Unified Data Integration
Sales play summary: Connect, integrate, transform and enrich IT &amp; OT data across structured, unstructured data - for data at rest and in motion. Sales play leverages Pentaho Data Integration and Pentaho Business Analytics.
"</nullif>
        <length>-1</length>
        <precision>-1</precision>
        <set_empty_string>N</set_empty_string>
      </field>
      <field>
